{"tid":1895301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：首批專機會將武漢市約450名香港居民接回港","createTime":"2020-02-24T12:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T15:01:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":167,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"ce09f4379729f610ff85e76d8f87ab5a55df6351","tid":1895301,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"政府宣布，將安排專機分批接回身處湖北省的港人回港。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權表示，細節仍然需要進一步協商，首批專機會協助武漢市的香港居民回港，亦會盡量安排身處湖北省其他地方，但情況較緊急的港人，坐首批專機回港。<br />\n<br />\n他說回港人士要入住檢疫中心14日，至於其他湖北省的港人，則要逐步作安排。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510525-20200224.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510525-20200224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwV8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=f54431c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510525-20200224.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=db36f9dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510525-20200224.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"979e66fe8a1c834b530f1524939b67123e46f2c8","tid":1895301,"uid":60052,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"14日? 屌你老母"},{"pid":"415601cd0e4c2f183622c07c5d828ef9d6cfce2e","tid":1895301,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"政府宣布，將安排專機分批接載湖北省香港居民回港。政制及內地事務局局長聶德權指，首批會接載在武漢市的約450名香港居民。在湖北省其他地方的香港居民，如果是孕婦、有嚴重病患需要動手術、或是文憑試考生等，亦希望可以首批接回香港，有關安排要和湖北省政府協商，上機的人要有香港身份證，有呼吸道病徵的人不適宜上機。"},{"pid":"6317b7af9f8e9e0716e43c99773db652f8ee3b2a","tid":1895301,"uid":337899,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"450粒退燒藥準備"},{"pid":"474f177a4f5338040a62a383d3b9a114c49db3ad","tid":1895301,"uid":11448,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"坐埋一齊 無病都變有<img src=\"/assets/